---
import AstroshipLayout from "../../layouts/AstroshipLayout.astro";
import Container from "../../components/container.astro";
import Button from "../../components/ui/button.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<AstroshipLayout
  title="Chelsea FC, The Jockey Club & The FA use Shout - Shout.com"
  description="Read why David Hollinshead would recommend Shout's advanced features, affordability, and responsive customer service."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <Container>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <a href="/customers/" class="hover:text-primary underline">← Back to Customer Testimonials</a>
      </p>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">David Hollinshead, Insight Lead</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight mb-4">
            Chelsea FC, The Jockey Club & The FA
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            David has worked with some of the most prestigious sports organisations in the United Kingdom, delivering data-driven insights to create a positive impact at a business-wide level.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
            In his most recent role, he performs market sizing and segmentation, tracks brand reputation, and conducts Net Promoter Score surveys for events across 15 venues.
          </p>
          <Button href="https://identity.shout.com/Account/Register">Start your free trial</Button>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            src="/images/2024/01/1686655085497.jpg"
            alt="David Hollinshead"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <Icon name="bx:bxs-quote-left" class="w-12 h-12 text-primary mx-auto mb-6" />
        <blockquote class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-6">
          "I came into the business with minimal budget and needing to convince senior people that a data lead approach was the way forward – Shout enabled me to do so."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-gray-600">David Hollinshead</p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- What David loves -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <Container>
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight">What David loves about Shout</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-gray-600">
          David has used Shout for his role as Insight Lead for The Jockey Club, The Football Association (FA), and Chelsea Football Club.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Icon name="bx:check-circle" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary mr-3" />
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Simplified workflows</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Shout's survey software stood out primarily because of its exceptional ease of use. User-friendly and intuitive in design.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Icon name="bx:palette" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary mr-3" />
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Consistent brand visibility</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            The flexibility in branding was a game-changer, allowing consistent brand experience across various touch points.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Icon name="bx:bar-chart-alt-2" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary mr-3" />
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Perfectly balanced reporting</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Shout consolidates intricate survey data into digestible visuals, making it easy to identify trends and patterns.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem solved -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <Container>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight mb-6">What problem Shout solved</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            When David joined the business, he faced the significant challenge of implementing a <strong>data-led approach on a minimal budget</strong>. Convincing senior stakeholders of the merits of this approach required not only a persuasive argument but also a tool that could effectively demonstrate value.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Shout not only aligned with budget constraints but also provided robust tools needed to make a compelling case for a data-led approach.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            The platform's <strong>user-friendly features and intuitive design</strong> allowed seamless integration of data into decision-making processes, showcasing the tangible benefits of leveraging insights for strategic planning.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            src="/images/2024/01/David-Hollinshead-Survey-Created-With-Shout.png"
            alt="Survey created with Shout"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- Why recommend -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <Container>
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight">Why David recommends Shout</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          The standout feature has been question logic. This adds a layer of sophistication to surveys, ensuring a personalized and efficient experience for participants.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Affordability was a key concern, and Shout excels in this regard. The platform strikes the perfect balance by being budget-friendly while refusing to compromise on features.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Another aspect that continuously impresses is the exemplary customer service. The team is not only quick to respond but also remarkably efficient in resolving any queries or issues.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-primary text-white">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Inspired by David?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8 opacity-90">
          Sign up with Shout to transform your business with a data-led approach. We have all the features you need, without asking you to break the bank.
        </p>
        <Button href="https://identity.shout.com/Account/Register" class="bg-white text-primary hover:bg-gray-100">Start creating surveys today</Button>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</AstroshipLayout>
